overview.en: Made in partnership with Gods Unchained Corporation, $GODS is the native ERC-20 token of the Gods Unchained universe. Mortals can use $GODS to craft NFTs, purchase packs from the Gods Unchained marketplace and earn even more rewards by holding the tokens in Immutable X.
overview.zh: GODS 与 Gods Unchained Corporation 合作制造，是 Gods Unchained 宇宙的原生 ERC-20 代币。凡人可以使用 $GODS 来制作 NFT，从 Gods Unchained 市场购买包并通过持有 Immutable X 中的代币获得更多奖励
